{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, this property is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two foci","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically, this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This property has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value other than "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view with an animated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transition. If you don’t want to animate the change, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"location is being tracked.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)targetCoordinate","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L752"},"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"targetCoordinate","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserTrackingMode/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse":{"abstract":[{"text":"The map follows the user location and rotates when the course changes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Course represents the direction in which the device is traveling.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The default user location annotation shows a puck-shaped indicator","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that rotates as the course changes.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnusertrackingmode\/mlnusertrackingmodefollowwithcourse","title":"MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","type":"topic","title":"MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/targetCoordinate":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate","kind":"symbol","title":"targetCoordinate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre"}}}